Package: WakjiraAgriStats
Type: Package
Title: Agricultural Experimental Design and ANOVA Toolkit
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Wakjira", "Tesfahun", email = "wakjiratesfahun@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for agricultural experimental designs including
    Completely Randomized Design (CRD), Randomized Complete Block Design (RCBD),
    Latin Square, factorial, split-plot, split-split, strip-plot designs,
    ANOVA, assumption diagnostics, and mean separation methods.
